 may include your\nemail address when you use your email address as your user name.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n<h3><b>Tracking,\nAnonymous Tracking, Do Not Track<\/b><\/h3>\n\n<p>Depending on your\nuser preferences, we may track your activities on Simplicity Studio by your\nuser ID or anonymously.  If we collect your data anonymously, your data will be\ncombined with data from all other users and will not be associated with you or\nyour user ID in any manner. If you set your user preferences to allow us to\ntrack you anonymously, your use and access to Simplicity Studio will be\nrestricted to &ldquo;unrestricted&rdquo; areas and files within Simplicity Studio.<\/p>\n\n<p>If you set your user\npreferences to &ldquo;Do not track&rdquo; we will not collect any data concerning your use\nof Simplicity Studio and your use and access to Simplicity Studio will be\nrestricted to &ldquo;unrestricted&rdquo; areas and files within Simplicity Studio.<\/p>\n\n<p>You may change your\nuser preferences concerning tracking at any time.  If you change your tracking\npreference to &ldquo;Anonymous&rdquo; we will remove your user ID from all information that\nwe collect from that time forward.  If you change your user preference to &ldquo;Do\nnot track&rdquo; we will not collect any data concerning your future use of\nSimplicity Studio.<\/p>\n\n<p>The information we\ncollect automatically is statistical data and may include personal information\nsuch as your user ID, or we may maintain it or associate it with personal\ninformation we collect in other ways or receive from third parties. It helps us\nto improve Simplicity Studio and to deliver a better and more personalized\nservice, including by enabling us to:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Estimate\nour audience size and usage patterns.<\/li>\n\n<li>Store\ninformation about your preferences, allowing us to customize Simplicity Studio\naccording to your individual interests.<\/li>\n\n<li>Remember\nyour user preferences.<\/li>\n\n<li>Recognize\nyou when you retu