t; feature of Simplicity\nStudio, we will transmit the contents of that email and your email address to\nthe recipients.<\/li>\n\n<li>For\nany other purpose disclosed by us when you provide the information.<\/li>\n\n<li>With\nyour consent.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>We may also disclose\nyour personal information:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>To\ncomply with any court order, law, or legal process, including to respond to any\ngovernment or regulatory request.<\/li>\n\n<li>To\nenforce or apply these Terms of Use.<\/li>\n\n<li>If\nwe believe disclosure is necessary or appropriate to protect our rights, property,\nor safety or that of our customers or other third parties. <\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n<h3><b>Choices\nAbout How We Collect Your Information<\/b><\/h3>\n\n<p>We strive to provide\nyou with choices regarding the personal information you provide to us. We have\ncreated mechanisms to provide you with the following control over your\ninformation: <\/p>\n\n<p>You can set your user preferences to\ncontrol whether and how we collect information concerning your use of\nSimplicity Studio.  You can set your User Experience as follows:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><b>Simplicity Studio login experience tracking<\/b> \u2013 We will collect information about your\nuser experience and it will be associated with your user ID.  You will have\naccess to all areas of Simplicity Studio.<\/li>\n\n<li>\n<b>Anonymous experience tracking<\/b>\n\u2013 We will collect information about your user experience and it will NOT be\nassociated with your user ID.  Your information will be combined with all\nothers users&rsquo; data.  You will have access only to unrestricted areas of\nSimplicity Studio.<\/li>\n\n<li>\n<b>Do not track experience<\/b>\n\u2013 We will not collect any information about your user experience.  You will\nhave access only to unrestricted areas of Simplicity Studio. <\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n<p>You can review and\nchange your personal information by logging into your account on the CRM. You\nmay access the Salesforce.com CRM at www.siliconlabs.force.com. <\/p>\n\n<p>You can change your\nUser Experience settings at any time. <\/p>\n\n<h3><b>Data\nSecurity<\/b><\/h3>\n\n<p>We have implemented\nmeasures designed to secure your personal information from accidental loss and\nfrom unauthorized access, use, alteration, and disclosure. All information you\nprovide to us is stored on our secure servers behind firewalls. <\/p>\n\n<p>The safety and\nsecurity of your information also depends on you. Where we have given you (or\nwhere you have chosen) a password for access to certain parts of Simplicity\nStudio, you are responsible for keeping this password confidential. We ask you\nnot to share your password with anyone.<\/p>\n\n<p>Unfortunately, the\ntransmission of information via the internet is not completely secure. Although\nwe do our best to protect your personal information, we cannot guarantee the security\nof your personal information transmitted to Simplicity Studio. Any transmission\nof personal information is at your own risk. We are not responsible for\ncircumvention of any privacy settings or security measures contained on\nSimplicity Studio. <\/p>\n\n<h3><b>Changes\nto Our Privacy Statement<\/b><\/h3>\n\n<p>It is our policy to\npost any changes we make to our Privacy Statement with a notice that the Terms\nof Use and Privacy Statement has been updated on Simplicity Studio home page.\nThe date the Terms of Use and Privacy Statement was last revised is identified\nat the top of the page.<\/p>\n\n<\/div>\n\n<\/body>\n\n<\/html>\n","id":2,"title":"Simplicity Studio Terms of Use and Privacy Statement"},{"softwareCovered":["Bundled JXBrowser Support 7.41.2"],"text":"<html>\n<head>\n<title>Chromium Redistribution License<\/title>\n<style>\n   P { font-family: \"Courier New\", Courier, monospace; }\n   H1 { font-size: 1.5em; }\n<\/style>\n<\/head>\n\n<body lang=EN-US>\n\n<div>\n\n<h1><b>Chromium Redistribution License<\/b><\/h1>\n\n   <p>\n\n      // Copyright 2015 The Chromium Author